cards.headline: Waanti baayyee barbaachisaan ati baratte maalidha?

cards.text: Tokkoon tokkoon keessan bilbila keessaniin, gaaffiif deebii hiriyaa keessanii wajjin geggeessaa, isa booda gaaffiif deebii innimmoo sii wajjin geggeessa.
Hiriyaakee gaafadhu, "Waanti baayyee barbaachisaan ati waa'ee qopheessa suur-sagalee baratte maalidha?"
Akka hiriyaakee dhageessutti itti dhiyaachuukee mirkaneeffadhu.
Sagaleen dudduubaa jeequ baayyeen yoo jiraate, bakka haaraa barbaadi.
Gaaffiif deebiikeef bakka mataa sirrii kennuu akka qabdu yaadadhu.

goals: Gaafadhu: Waanti baayyee barbaachisaan ati waa'ee qopheessa suur-sagalee baratte maalidha?

cards.text: Yoo muraalee baayyee waraabde, maxxansuu keen dura muraa filatte qofa hambisuudhaan kan hafan haqi.
Hin yaadda'in, muraan hundi kuusaa faayaa keessa taa'a.

title: Waanti baayyee barbaachisaan ati baratte maalidha?
